ISLAMABAD, Sep 22 (APP):Deputy Speaker Qasim Khan Suri Tuesday urged the people to fully participate in the ongoing anti-polio campaign to save their children from the devastating and crippling disease and give them a bright and healthy future.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said during the anti-polio campaign that started from September 21, 40 million children will be administered the anti-polio drops.
